name: abstraction of sun glasses #0 [100 megapixel]
description:
This video artwork is autonomously generated by AI algorithms of the input term 'sun glasses'. 
The resulting work is an interpretation how artificial intelligence might see our world: colorful, shimmering and slightly psychedelic.
The artwork is unique and not repeatable, because chance plays a part and every algorithm run produces a different artifact.

The resolution of the digital image is 10.000 by 10.000 pixel. So can be printed really really big!
